# Model Performance Improvement Across Ecoregions
# Scatter plot of OA, F1, Kappa improvement by ecoregion
# Corresponds to Fig. 4 in the manuscript

"""
OVERVIEW
This notebook visualizes the performance improvement of the TST-EC model 
compared to the Global model across 31 Chinese ecoregions.

METHODOLOGY
1. Loads model performance metrics (OA, F1, Kappa) for both models
2. Calculates improvement values (TST-EC minus Global)
3. Creates scatter plot showing all three metrics
4. Analyzes regional patterns of improvement

METRICS ANALYZED
1. Overall Accuracy (OA) - General classification accuracy
2. F1 Score - Harmonic mean of precision and recall  
3. Kappa Coefficient - Agreement accounting for chance

KEY FINDINGS
- Most ecoregions show positive improvement across all metrics
- Kappa improvement is most pronounced
- Regional variations in model performance improvement
"""

# ============================================================================
# ENVIRONMENT SETUP
# ============================================================================

import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')

# Set publication style
plt.rcParams['font.family'] = 'Arial'
plt.rcParams['font.size'] = 12
plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False
sns.set_style("whitegrid")

# ============================================================================
# DATA PREPARATION
# ============================================================================

